# Contribution

## Formatting
To abide by the formatting of the source code, make sure your `hxformat.json` has this as the bare minimum

```json
{
	"lineEnds": {
		"leftCurly": "after",
		"rightCurly": "both",
		"objectLiteralCurly": {
			"leftCurly": "after"
		}
	},
	"sameLine": {
		"ifElse": "next",
		"doWhile": "next",
		"tryBody": "next",
		"tryCatch": "next"
	}
}
```
## Pull Requests
Make sure your commits are descriptive, mention what you are implementing and how it will improve the library or fix an issue with it.


